ompared with a large number of state of the\nart algorithms. Furthermore we illustrate how DBRM can be used for model\ninference in various applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jun 2018 13:13:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jun 2018 09:41:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-08"}
